parameters: "Oh? The movements of these tentacles seem odd."

"(These tentacles, they're the main body nesting in the
cave... the boss.)"

"(With so many tentacles covering the cave, I thought there
must be something... I see, there are multiple boss
tentacles.)"

"It feels a bit dangerous, so could you defeat them
quickly?"

"(It seems Maroges hasn't realized that completing the
request by defeating this boss will end it.)"

"(This is my chance. If I defeat all these tentacles before
they realize they're the main body...)"

"(The contract of servitude itself will be nullified upon
completion of the request. Then, capturing Maroges himself
will be easy.)"
Tina: "I'll finish this quickly. Stand back."
"An opponent of this level is no enemy to me."

The boss tentacles keep appearing one after another from the
ground.

Not just the parts visible to the eye, but dozens of boss
tentacles made up this tentacle cave.

Furthermore, do the other tentacles have regenerative
abilities? Tentacles grow back from where they were cut.

However, Tina attacks the newly appeared tentacles with
blinding speed, visibly reducing their number.

Tina puts more strength into her body and accelerates her
movements even further.

Suddenly, Tina's blade-type weapon cracks and shatters to
pieces.
"Oh dear, it seems to have broken."

Tina's blade-type weapon is of the highest quality,
including physical resistance.

Adjusted by Suelle, it's a blade that should hardly ever get
scratched, let alone shatter into pieces without warning.

Glaring at Maroges, who likely tampered with it the night
before, Tina lunges at him in anger.

"(Damn, the tentacles are regenerating faster than I
thought!!)"

Tina somehow deflects the surprise tentacle attacks from the
ground with her broken blade.

"I would like to refute these baseless suspicions...
However, shouldn't we prioritize defeating these tentacles
first?"

"(I can take down monsters of this level with my bare
hands.)"

"(That's right, stay calm. If I defeat the tentacles, the
contract of servitude with Maroges should be broken.)"
"(Once that's done, I can capture that man anytime!!)"

Deciding to deal with Maroges after handling the tentacles,
Tina focuses on the tentacles and raises her fist.
The sound of a swift movement!

However, Tina's fist, swung with the intent to strike,
misses the tentacles by a hair's breadth and cuts through
the air.
But it was not because the tentacles dodged.
The sound of a heavy fall!
"(What?! My body's strength is draining away...)"

"(Is this the effect of the servitude contract that
activates when I try to harm Maroges?)"

"(Don't tell me... just because I tried to grab Maroges
earlier, it was judged as an attack!!?)"

Unable to muster any strength, Tina is gradually engulfed by
the tentacles.
HP and MP have been fully restored.
